N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4812.5 - License form

State Regulations

The clerk of the municipality shall issue a license on
form BC-5 as prescribed by the commission. In the case of limited period bingo
the clerk shall enter thereon the charge for a single opportunity to
participate in one game. Notes
